==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: fēn jiŭ bì hé, hé jiŭ bì fēn
===Proverb===
'''[[分]][[久]][[必]][[合]]，[[合]][[久]][[必]][[分]]'''
# After a long split, a union will occur; after a long union, a split will occur.

